laced heredity as the determining factor in who should run a firm=E2=80=94a=
nd
probably for the better. Companies such as JPMorgan Chase (market value $75=
0 billion) are far more profitable and powerful as public entities than the=
y ever were as discrete private partnerships.<br/><br/>That=E2=80=99s what =
